    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="grc">
                    <ab>
                        <lb n="1"/>εἰκόνι χαλκείῃ σε Πρόβον
                        <lb n="2"/>τὸν ὕπαρχον Ἀθήναις
                        <lb n="3"/>Ἀντόλιος σ<supplied reason="omitted">τῆσ</supplied>εν Ἑλλάδος ἀνθύπατος.
                    </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
                <p>Edition based on IG.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <p>“With a bronze statue, you, Probus, praefect, in Athens Anatolius, proconsul of Greece (i.e. Achaia), has set up.”</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="fr">
                <p>“...”</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="it">
                <p>“Con una statua bronzea, te, Probus, prefetto, ad Atene Anatolius, proconsole della Grecia (<foreign>i.e. </foreign>Achaia), ha posto.”</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The dedication was made when Probus was praetorian prefect for the first time.</p>
            </div>
